  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK526">
<l>peruṅkoṭaiyāṉ pēṇāṉ vekuḷi yavaṉiṉ</l>
<l>maruṅkuṭaiyār mānilat til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>No one, in all the world, will have so many relatives (about him), as he who makes large gift, and does not give way to anger.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
